lso I mean not to nitpick but the incidence of lost bank dollars is a whole=
 lot lower than the incidence of lost Bitcoins.[8] I guess I did.=C2=A0=E2=
=80=9CIf Robinhood was legally obligated to let you buy all the stocks you =
want whenever you want, it would have been sued into oblivion long ago,=E2=
