</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The only cryptocurrency that I own is =
ExcelCoin.[1] ExcelCoin is a=C2=A0next-generation cryptocurrency whose cent=
ral innovation is=C2=A0that its ledger is maintained not by proof of work, =
which is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26319066.=
271646/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2VtaW5pLmNvbS9jcnlwdG9wZWRpYS9iaXRjb2luLW1pbmluZy1j=
