n the gas fees. Payment fees by credit card, which typically feel extortion=
ary, look cheap compared to that. OpenSea could even publish a simple trans=
parency log if people wanted a public record of transactions, offers, bids,=
 etc to verify their accounting.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">However, i=
f they had built a platform to buy and sell images that wasn=E2=80=99t nomi=
